	<Title>
		Need exercise motivation? Put it on paper
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Are you hoping that exercise will help you lose weight? Boost your energy? Sleep better? Manage a chronic condition? Improve your mood? Write it down! Seeing the benefits of regular exercise on paper may help you stay motivated.&lt;/p&gt;
